high_descs: Turn around and walk out of the room. Turn left and walk down the hall. Turn left and enter the bedroom.
Walk to the desk and pick up the green book from the desk.
Turn around and walk out of the bedroom. Turn to the right and enter the cabinet with the closet.
Open the cabinet and put the book in the cabinet. Close the cabinet door.
Turn around and leave the room. Turn to the left and walk back to the bedroom. Walk to the desk.
Pick up the book with red on it from the desk.
Turn around and walk out of the bedroom. Turn right and walk to the cabinet with the closet.
Open the cabinet and put the book inside of it, to the right of the green book. Close the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Move the two books from the bedroom desk and put them in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the desk.
Pick up book from the desk.
Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the cabinet.
Place book on the cabinet.
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near desk.
Pick up book from the desk.
Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the cabinet.
Place book on the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Collecting book from different places and arranging them on a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around to exit the room and turn left to head down the passage and turn left to reach the desk.
Pick up the green book from the table.
Turn around and exit the room on the left and head down the passage and turn right to reach the cabinet on the right.
Put the green book in the cabinet.
Turn around to exit the room and turn left to head down the passage and turn left to reach the desk.
Pick up the white book from the table.
Turn around and exit the room on the left and head down the passage and turn right to reach the cabinet on the right.
Put the white book in the cabinet with the other book.
anns.task_desc: Put two books in the cabinet.
